OL,3,CMinisters to launch review into
OL,4,Cheadlight glare as drivers report
OL,5,Cbeing dazzled
OL,7,FResearch into headlight glare is to be
OL,8,Flaunched amid concerns about drivers
OL,9,Fbeing dazzled, the has announced.
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport (DfT)
OL,12,Fsaid independent research will be
OL,13,Fcommissioned to "better understand the
OL,14,Froot causes of driver glare and
OL,15,Fidentify any further appropriate
OL,16,Fmitigations".
OL,18,FIt comes in response to a petition
OL,19,Fwith more than 10,000 signatures which
OL,20,Furged ministers to launch a review "to
OL,21,Ffind solutions".
