OL,7,FThe , which has campaigned on the
OL,8,Fissue, said the topic "struck a chord
OL,9,Fwith motorists" and the study will be
OL,10,Fa "golden opportunity" to "get to the
OL,11,Fbottom of the problem".
OL,13,FA recent survey commissioned by the
OL,14,FRAC suggested 85% drivers affected by
OL,15,Fheadlight glare believe the problem is
OL,16,Fgetting worse.
OL,18,FThe poll of 2,000 UK drivers also
OL,19,Findicated that 89% think some car
OL,20,Fheadlights are too bright.
