OL,7,FIt found 67% of those affected by
OL,8,Fheadlight glare said being dazzled
OL,9,Fforces them to slow down considerably,
OL,10,Fwhile 64% believe some headlights are
OL,11,Fso bright they risk causing accidents.
OL,13,FIn January, ITV News Consumer Editor
OL,14,FChris Choi reported on the findings of
OL,15,Fthe RAC poll
