OL,7,FThe RAC believes headlights appear
OL,8,Fbrighter on modern cars because the
OL,9,Fuse of LED rather than traditional
OL,10,Fhalogen bulbs creates a more intense
OL,11,Fand focused beam, which improves a
OL,12,Fdriver's view but can be to the
OL,13,Fdetriment of other road users.
OL,15,FOther potential factors include badly
OL,16,Faligned headlights and the increase in
OL,17,Fthe number of cars that sit higher on
OL,18,Fthe road, such as SUVs
