OL,7,FIn its response to the petition, the
OL,8,FDfT also said international rules
OL,9,Frequiring new cars to have mandatory
OL,10,Fautomatic headlight levelling based on
OL,11,Fthe weight being carried were agreed
OL,12,Fby the United Nations in April last
OL,13,Fyear and will come into force in
OL,14,FSeptember 2027.
OL,16,FThe department expressed its belief
OL,17,Fthat "these tougher requirements will
OL,18,Fhelp alleviate the number of cases
OL,19,Fwhere road users are dazzled".
