OL,7,FGovernment figures show that since
OL,8,F2013 there have been an average of 280
OL,9,Fcollisions on Britain's roads every
OL,10,Fyear where dazzling headlights were a
OL,11,Fcontributory factor.
OL,13,FOf these, six a year involved someone
OL,14,Flosing their life.
OL,16,FRAC road safety spokesman Rod Dennis
OL,17,Fsaid: "The fact the government has
OL,18,Flistened to drivers' concerns and
OL,19,Fheeded our calls to examine the
OL,20,Fcomplex issue of headlight glare in
OL,21,Fmore detail marks a real turning point.
